<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Welcome to Topia Rank's Newest Product</title>
</head>
<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; margin: 0; padding: 0;">
    <header style="background-color: #f5f5f5; padding: 20px;">
        <h1 style="margin: 0; font-size: 24px; color: #333;">Welcome to Topia Rank's Newest Product</h1>
    </header>
    <main style="padding: 20px;">
        <section>
            <h2 style="font-size: 20px; margin-bottom: 10px;">Dear <%= name %> owner,</h2>
            <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6;">I hope this email finds you well. I understand that you are busy, but I wanted to take a moment to inform you about our latest service that is now available. This service has the potential to enhance your productivity and make a positive impact on your life.</p>
            <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6;">We invite you to explore this new offering and discover how it can benefit you.</p>
            <a href="<%= url %>" style="
                background-color: #00aaff;
                color: white;
                text-decoration: none;
                padding: 10px 20px;
                border-radius: 5px;
                display: inline-block;
                margin-top: 20px;
                transition: background-color 0.3s;
            ">Take a Look</a>
        </section>
    </main>
    <footer style="background-color: #f5f5f5; padding: 20px; text-align: center;">
        <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 14px; color: #666;">Thank you for your attention.</p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
